thread.title: Jack Kasady
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Jack Kasady

author: Jack Kasady
title: Jack Kasady
text: Was our first time ordering from Ink Station & there was a bit of a mixup with delivery but I gave them a call & was fixed within minutes,very impressed. I also made an enquiry as to whether they stocked a certain size ink as I couldn't see it online & it was no problem for them to find out for me. Will definitely order again..
